<% layout('Boilerplate.ejs') %>
<div class="header header--vision-mission">
  <div class="header__text-box"> 
    <div class="heading-primary">
      <span class="heading-primary--main">vision & mission</span>
      <span class="heading-primary--sub">the where and the why</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="text-container">
  <div class="u-margin-top-medium">
    <h3 class="heading-secondary"> vision </h3>
  </div>
  <p class="text-container__paragraph u-margin-top-small">
    We envision imparting domain relevant skills through customized learning by providing a
    conducive environment that facilitates multifaceted development of the student.
  </p>
  <div class="u-margin-top-medium">
    <h3 class="heading-secondary"> mission </h3>
  </div>
  <p class="text-container__paragraph u-margin-top-small">
    Our mission is to develop the youth by bridging the gap between academia and industry
    through an activity based curriculum which focuses on collective and collaborative
    learning across different domains.
  </p>
  <div class="text-container__list u-margin-top-medium">
    <div class="u-margin-bottom-small">
      <h2 class="heading-secondary">objective</h2>            
    </div>
    <ul class="text-list">
      <li class="text-list__item"> To promote meaningful learning that enhances decision making skills and builds confidence</li>
      <li class="text-list__item"> To make undergraduates resourceful through activity and problem based learning</li>
      <li class="text-list__item"> To expand and diversify the initial thought process by providing practical exposure</li>
      <li class="text-list__item"> To provide relevant and domain specific technical and industrial awareness</li>
      <li class="text-list__item"> To impart hands on experience to students through interactive workshops by industry experts and professionals</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>